{"tid":1907953,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：本港疫情仍然「可控」","createTime":"2020-03-03T02:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T04:25:40.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4d57bb17f080aa1fbb345fe6e8c6dc60fc7998ec","tid":1907953,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T02:57:41.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥在行政會議前表示，目前本港的疫情仍然可控，但不能掉以輕心，政府已因應疫情蔓延多國，對相關國家採取旅遊限制，強調特區政府在防控工作不會放鬆，既要防止病毒輸入香港，亦要防止病毒在本地傳播，呼籲市民保持個人衛生，減少社交接觸，包括聚會及聚餐活動，強調每位市民的努力，都有助打贏這場疫戰。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1270826&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1270826%26csid%3D261_341&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BOL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=3f9d9648\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1270826&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"30e0faad7fb19a8c319d123684ce7753bf2e1100","tid":1907953,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T02:58:00.000Z","msg":"pull"},{"pid":"ae4e963fececa35cf25c2f7194f5d914b1565ae2","tid":1907953,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:05:21.000Z","msg":"同支那口吻一致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff00ff30fb5810d1f0a19613ba0ccdb3acdb0265","tid":1907953,"uid":224533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:22:42.000Z","msg":"柒婆邏輯: 未可控就唔戴罩，可控就戴罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36134435c6dd1e0eff87f3b74689815534aa41b4","tid":1907953,"uid":262700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:25:38.000Z","msg":"因為目前可控, 所以要復工令佢失控"},{"pid":"fe3235aa9337616cb27aae8d507db0251750233f","tid":1907953,"uid":57636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:27:28.000Z","msg":"佢講嘢又學返張局長行精簡路線?<br />\n如果香港班官生於智利會點<img src=\"/ass